                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A chomurk can fly as a full action at the listed speed. It must move in a straight line while flying in this way, and it can use the Piloting skill instead of Acrobatics to fly in difficult or dangerous conditions.",
                "name": "Biothruster",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex"
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A chomurk can use its biothruster as a ranged weapon with the line and unwieldy weapon special properties and a total range of 40 feet. Though the jet of flame deals fire damage, it is also treated as having the force descriptor.",
                "name": "Flame Jet",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex"
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A hive of at least 32 chomurks can meld their bodies together in a unique metamorphosis that amplifies their natural thruster abilities. Chomurks combined in this manner dissolve and merge their limbs in a process that takes 1 hour, creating a pyramidal mound of bodies that acts as a single huge thruster capable of altering the orbit of the asteroid, space station, ship, or similarly sized astronomical body upon which it resides. Chomurks combined in this manner become a single entity, but are otherwise helpless and rely on nonmerged chomurks to defend them.",
                "name": "Move Worlds",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su"
